The storage engine, LogsQL query language, application layer, agent, and
tooling were ported from the Go sources of VictoriaLogs and its
VictoriaMetrics library dependencies to Rust by Softalink LLC. Product names,
binary names, HTTP headers, metric prefixes, and identifiers were rebranded
(VictoriaLogs -> EsLogs, vl/vm prefixes -> esl/esm); references to upstream
documentation and source URLs are retained where they remain factual.
